<h2 id="扫描并列出-wifi-热点">扫描并列出 WIFI 热点</h2>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh"><span class="line hl"><span class="ln">1</span><span class="cl">nmcli device wifi rescan
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="ln">2</span><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line hl"><span class="ln">3</span><span class="cl">nmcli device wifi list
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="ln">4</span><span class="cl">IN-USE BSSID SSID MODE CHAN RATE SIGNAL BARS SECURITY 
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="ln">5</span><span class="cl"> 80:8F:1D:73:F1:21 <span class="m">403</span> FORBIDDEN Infra <span class="m">1</span> <span class="m">405</span> Mbit/s <span class="m">100</span> ▂▄▆█ WPA1 WPA2 
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="ln">6</span><span class="cl"> 24:69:68:64:B4:F1 RAZON WIFI Infra <span class="m">11</span> <span class="m">405</span> Mbit/s <span class="m">100</span> ▂▄▆█ WPA1 WPA2 
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="ln">7</span><span class="cl"> .....
</span></span></code></pre></div>

<h2 id="连接-wifi-热点">连接 WIFI 热点</h2>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh"><span class="line"><span class="ln">1</span><span class="cl">nmcli device wifi connect <span class="s2">&#34;&lt;SSID&gt;&#34;</span>
</span></span></code></pre></div>

<p>将其中的 <code>&lt;SSID&gt;</code> 替换为附近的 WIFI 热点，比如上诉例子的 <code>RAZON WIFI</code>，然后按提示输入密码即可。</p>